comments: Theres a reason why out of 30 people in the class, we were left with 8 regulars at the end. He has those who he prefers(these are the only people who he can name) which isnt helpful if he needs to tell you how you improved in your speech, since he cant remember your speeches. Also talks way too much about the same things.
One of my best teachers ever!!

Simple class. He makes it easy to talk infront of other people, even though I didnt have a problem with public speaking before. He does go off about random things sometimes. We had about 8 speeches planned, but only did like 4 because he talks so much during class. Either way, the class wasnt bad at all.
This is a really nice guy.
Mr. Garfinkel is a great teacher!!! He realizes how hard it is for some people to speack in public, and helps build your confidence!!!
MR. G IS THE BEST SPEECH PROF AT WESTERN
